## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. The understanding of gender identity is continually evolving, and new research may further expand or refine current perspectives. Additionally, cultural differences in the perception of gender identity were not extensively covered, which may influence the applicability of these findings across different societies.